Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛米羅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我帶你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛米羅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所嚮往的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也追不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以甩下過去的速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…向著那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時間居然還有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作和時間可沒關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始不想當殺手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天撿了一部壞掉了的錄影機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想試試能不能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買部新的不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣多浪費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還能用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能用…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早去早回啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想分開  想一直待在玲二身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是還能回來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候退出了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是洗手不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是逃之夭夭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  利茲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利茲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利茲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  我真是老在拖你後腿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是聽說了哦  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那個Phantom呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪我那些年輕的兄弟這麼輕易地就被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必再演戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是拿著證據的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙幹的好事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒話好說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梧桐先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那照片是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你醜態畢露之前還是聽我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:05:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道這是上頭要你幹的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是想找到黑幕而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們受的三次襲擊都是克勞迪婭指使的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒說錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你腦子沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為克勞迪婭為了讓你們加入Inferno費了多少心思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也不討厭那些忠誠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那女人可不是值得你們效忠到這種地步的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被耍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡說八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  這位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是第一次在這裡見面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是個值得回憶的夜晚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  到現在都快一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  哪個組織的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貨被…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能高興得太早哦  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  原來是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們和賽斯聯手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯我可不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安排這事兒的可是克勞迪婭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們走投無路的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人突然跑來跟我們磋商
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們搶到500公斤的古柯鹼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事前的準備都做好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接應的人也安排好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還跟我們說「要不要在洛杉磯大鬧一番呢？」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:07:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件是等這事平息後  梧桐組要通過她介紹加盟Inferno
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們最初也不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但知道那個女人的立場之後還是想明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人很想在Inferno裡擁有能當自己後盾的集團
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一直獨來獨往
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一輩子都沒有出人頭地的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前都是從別的地方購入貨物那都是胡說八道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梧桐組的整個市場都是我在這一年裡搶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以欠你們的古柯鹼為本錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  克勞迪婭把賽斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  有個呆子在那起事件中受到了牽連呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個傢伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說的那個賽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:08:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急變  賽斯背叛組織了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Phantom去襲擊了Inferno的貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織現在正全力搜索這兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都還沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有證明自己的清白  奪回Ein的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話該明白吧  這東西的用法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都和她有關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此  我們受傷  流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是有點頭緒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎？  Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來聞名天下的Phantom也過不了美人關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊  這件事還有後文呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人到最後還想把志賀和我拋下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接掌握梧桐組啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊為滅口把我們幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊還趁亂把自己的對手也消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道她腹黑到什麼程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？那個女人把我們當踏板了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不管Inferno什麼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被欺負成這樣還不做聲我就不叫梧桐大輔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信  我可不相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這卑鄙下流的盜賊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上車  Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛倫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛…愛倫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到  你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼？  愛倫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要這麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼愛倫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是從前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只是個Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno馬上就會來追殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次會徹底地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛倫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛倫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管現在還是從前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯·瑪斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梧桐組  克勞迪婭·瑪秋奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有Inferno的艾扎克·懷斯梅爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離間三者使他們互相猜疑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將曾經陷害過你的人一個又一個地送進地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的真相由我的安排傳達給了Inferno
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們將會立刻採取行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:13:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹殺叛徒克勞迪婭·瑪秋奈以及其心腹Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織要除掉我？這樣一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  通過了嗎  入學考試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你啊  美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想立刻告訴叔叔  直接過來沒打擾您工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過很辛苦吧  貿易的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  挺辛苦的  後天還得離開日本去進貨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什麼禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了啦  老麻煩您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要是收您太多禮物的話  會讓媽媽知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我約好朋友去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得開心點吧  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是離婚了  美緒也流著跟我和組長一樣的血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梧桐之鬼的血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人對她心懷不軌的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不知情的美緒就連自己都保護不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是變了立場還是改了姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙都是我的妹妹  重要的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志賀  這次是大生意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我不能活著回國的話  到時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒小姐前進的道路  我志賀會一直看到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  志賀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打中了肚子和肩膀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我吃了這兩倍以上的子彈都撐過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修羅道才是我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  到頭來又只剩下我和你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼時候都是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是什麼樣的地獄  你都跟我一起闖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的膽量和你的智慧  不管什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  克勞迪婭那邊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno會幹掉那個女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  我們梧桐組才是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno絕不會饒恕在那女人麾下的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始戰爭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno算什麼  騙了我們的帳  讓他們好好還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為這幫傢伙送上一場追悼戰  對吧志賀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們全都殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再死一個  就能擺平這一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志賀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今再說什麼或許您都不會再相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥  志賀是真心地仰慕您的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志賀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志賀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將造反的人清除掉表明了梧桐組的誠意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno就由我來幫你們搭線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志賀先生  這樣一來梧桐組就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋瑟培  我現在壓抑不住想對你開槍的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對我開槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我跟你還有商量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以成為好朋友  志賀先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞  你在哪啊克勞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪啊  在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少給我個藉口吧  克勞迪婭·瑪秋奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑吧  玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真不膩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:19:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會膩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那曲子你就那麼喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是最喜歡的人送的東西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來認為自己什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的人都理所當然擁有的東西我都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直認為自己不會得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一直待在玲二身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.88,0:23:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告  對決
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如這個世界不是無盡的地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為有你活著
